::KitKat::

She heard Drillbit and replied. "I'm currently in a meeting. I'll be 
right there when I"m done here." She turned off her link so she 
wouldn't be disturbed. She looked at Killfest, grinning slightly. She 
liked the idea of a nice group of heavy muscle on her side. Most of 
the bots on her team were her size, as was her enemies. But now, she 
would have the advantage of sheer muscle on her side.
